subject: Evp isnt just one or two words anymore!
author: Misty
full_text:
Not sure it ever was. I had a good group session the other day so 
thought I would share some of what came thru with the online crowd. A 
few are too long sentence wise to post here so I stuck them in my 
esnips account. They were pretty well spoken (for my ears) and I was 
pleasantly surprised at the depth of the messages that came thru.

http://www.esnips.com/web/SweepTuningEVP

Misty

http://misty.xm.com
